This package builds on (does not modify) agent-browser:

  agent-browser — https://agent-browser.dev
  Source: https://github.com/vercel-labs/agent-browser
  License: Apache License 2.0
  Pinned version: 0.31.0

agent-browser is used unmodified as an internal engine, invoked as a child
process behind the Lattice engine-adapter. Per ADR 0002, the agent-browser
daemon/CLI is internal-only and never directly reachable by an agent; its
kernel-bypassing primitives (eval, raw CDP/connect, file access, profile/state
import) are firewalled at the Lattice layer.

